Introduction:-
--------------------------
Hystrix is used to implement Circuit Breaker Pattern.

Hystrix provides fault and latency tolerance.

Hystrix isolates the points of access between the services.

It stops cascading failures across them and provides the fallback options.

Annotaion used :-
---------------------------
@EnableHystrix - is used to enable hystrix functionalites in Spring Boot application
@EnableHystrixDashboard - Optional feature of hystrix to monitor its status on a dashboard
@EnableCircuitBreaker
@HystrixCommand
@HystrixProperty
